{"tid":2133385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14議會60議員譴責 促國際聯手反制  彭定康：港府野蠻政治清洗","createTime":"2020-07-31T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T13:26:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7adbf032b1f85f1e39250a06e2fc4fade3519387","tid":2133385,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/DDJO5CSHCZWMXKORPJYSBAVFAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FDDJO5CSHCZWMXKORPJYSBAVFAA%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG15FIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=6f6c2198\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FDDJO5CSHCZWMXKORPJYSBAVFAA%2F&h=5d22953f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/DDJO5CSHCZWMXKORPJYSBAVFAA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n14議會60議員譴責 促國際聯手反制 <br />\n彭定康：港府野蠻政治清洗<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法生效一個月，12名民主派立法會選舉參選人被選舉主任裁定提名無效，事件引起國際關注。末代港督彭定康批評港府瘋狂取消民主派參選資格的行徑是野蠻的政治清洗；14地議會的議員亦同聲譴責，敦促國際以相應措施應對香港自由被收窄；英國外相藍韜文亦發表聲明，譴責DQ民主派參選人參加立法會選舉的決定。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康發聲明表示，「這是對香。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XCuEjq2w_-vdz7sRjj1AHCxCr38=/3012x2008/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UGHMASFYFCDP2FPOKEJN7ZNM3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXCuEjq2w_-vdz7sRjj1AHCxCr38%3D%2F3012x2008%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUGHMASFYFCDP2FPOKEJN7ZNM3M.jpg&h=c5f99a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前港督彭定康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文斥破壞兩制完整性<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：恐全軍覆沒 公民黨誓與港人並肩<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文亦發聲明，譴責取消反對派參選人參加立法會選舉的決定，指「他們（民主派參選人）顯然由於政治觀點被取消資格，這破壞了一國兩制的完整性，以及《中英聯合聲明》和《香港基本法》所保障的權利和自由」。他要求香港當局必須恪守對香港市民的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n由英國保守黨前黨魁、上議院議員施志安今年。。。。。。。。。。權利和自由的進一步縮窄。<br />\n<br />\n英國影子亞太國務大臣金諾克在Twitter稱，前日香港四名學生被指違反國安法被。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jjsNkgvNaV2lacsTFOBHuAqmb_k=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P273FYWH6XI7GYZAOTO6ZIRZ2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjjsNkgvNaV2lacsTFOBHuAqmb_k%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP273FYWH6XI7GYZAOTO6ZIRZ2Y.jpg&h=9d5786ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英外相藍韜文<br />\n<br />\n「有史以來最大規模鎮壓」<br />\n<br />\n人權組織「香港監察」總監帕德森形容，對溫和民主派人士的政治篩選，令新現狀成為現實，「議員反對國安法被指違憲的說法完全荒謬，國際間政府須對攻擊香港自由的行為作適當反應」。國際特赦組織就指港府針對反對派所為違反言論及結社自由，「很可能會加深香港的恐懼和緊張氣氛」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣執政民進黨指港府用各種。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國際傳媒都有報道有關消息，路透社。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/中央社"},{"pid":"fde22c8e0315b7fe1abb212f4f4fa7998c37c025","tid":2133385,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d313e5633be975aafe093719efb3cc5eb13d9d","tid":2133385,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}